init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He didn't know what was going on, but suddenly his "#1 Dad" mug changed to show that he was actually not ranked "#1."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He went to talk to his friends about it and they started experiencing the same thing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The whole world was confused and perplexed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He thought that if he figured out why, then he might be able to change it back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and his friends started to dig up information and asked a lot of questions.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If he saved his son from getting hit by a car, then that was what gave him the boost.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After this, Bob and his friends started to figure out ways to get a boost in their rankings.
